{
  "title": "OAuth 2.0",
  "order": 3,
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "p",
      "content": "DSP supports OAuth 2.0 authentication using Salesforce security features, including:"
    },
    {
      "type": "ul",
      "children": [
        { "type": "p", "content": "<strong>External Client App</strong>" },
        { "type": "p", "content": "<strong>Auth. Provider</strong>" },
        { "type": "p", "content": "<strong>Named Credential</strong>" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "content": "Follow the steps below to configure OAuth 2.0 authentication."
    },
    {
      "type": "h2",
      "content": "1. Create External Client App (Remote Org)",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "image",
          "content": "image/connection/OAuth-2/create-external-client-app/00.png",
          "alt": "Create External Client App"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "content": "image/connection/OAuth-2/create-external-client-app/1.png",
          "alt": "External Client App Details",
          "caption": ["Replace Contact Email with your email."]
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "content": "image/connection/OAuth-2/create-external-client-app/2.png",
          "alt": "External Client App OAuth Settings",
          "caption": ["Use a temporary URL for the Callback URL."]
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "content": "image/connection/OAuth-2/create-external-client-app/3.png",
          "alt": "External Client App Created"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "h2",
      "content": "2. Create Auth. Provider (DSP Installed Org)",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "image",
          "content": "image/connection/OAuth-2/create-auth-provider/0.png",
          "alt": "Create Auth Provider"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "content": "image/connection/OAuth-2/create-auth-provider/1.png",
          "alt": "Auth Provider Configuration",
          "caption": [
            "Copy and paste the Consumer Key and Consumer Secret from the remote org: Setup -> External Client App Manager -> The External App created previously -> Settings -> OAuth Settings -> Consumer Key and Secret.",
            "Scope: Use \"refresh_token full\" or any scopes you need."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "content": "image/connection/OAuth-2/create-auth-provider/2.png",
          "alt": "Auth Provider Callback URL",
          "caption": ["Copy the Callback URL."]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "h2",
      "content": "3. Update Callback URL (Remote Org)",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "image",
          "content": "image/connection/OAuth-2/update-callback-url/0.png",
          "alt": "Update Callback URL"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "h2",
      "content": "4. Create Named Credential (DSP Installed Org)",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "image",
          "content": "image/connection/OAuth-2/create-named-credential/0.png",
          "alt": "Create Named Credential"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "content": "image/connection/OAuth-2/create-named-credential/1.png",
          "alt": "Named Credential Configuration",
          "caption": [
            "URL: the domain URL of the remote org. This can be found in \"My Domain Settings\".",
            "Scope: Use \"refresh_token full\" or any scopes you need."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "h2",
      "content": "5. Create DSP Connection (DSP Installed Org)",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "image",
          "content": "image/connection/OAuth-2/create-connection/0.png",
          "alt": "Create Connection"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "h2",
      "content": "6. Test Connection",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "image",
          "content": "image/connection/OAuth-2/test-connection/0.png",
          "alt": "Test Connection"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
